Step 1: Start  
Step 2: Import random module  
Step 3: Create word list  
Step 4: Randomly select a word  
Step 5: Initialize attempts and guessed letters  
Step 6: Display hidden word  
Step 7: Take user input  
Step 8: Validate input  
Step 9: Check guessed letter  
Step 10: Update game status  
Step 11: Repeat until win/loss  
Step 12: End  

